---
title: SuperQuick Chipotle Grilled Chicken Tacos with Creamy Slaw and Feta
description: These quick and tasty chipotle chicken tacos are kissed by the grill and topped with a zesty, creamy slaw! A quick dinner can also be a grilled dinner.

